JAMES RIGATO: Yeah.

00:11:59.130 --> 00:12:00.540
I think for me, food--

00:12:00.540 --> 00:12:01.495
I don't know.

00:12:01.495 --> 00:12:02.726
It's like purpose, right?

00:12:02.726 --> 00:12:04.725
I grew up in a Catholic
school, which is ironic,

00:12:04.725 --> 00:12:06.000
because I grew up
in a trailer park,

