And for those of you who
haven't been to Mabel Gray yet,

00:18:33.623 --> 00:18:37.450
the menu changes daily
based on ingredients

00:18:37.450 --> 00:18:40.721
and I guess whatever you feel
like cooking for the day, maybe

00:18:40.721 --> 00:18:41.220
barbecue.

00:18:41.220 --> 00:18:41.370
JAMES RIGATO: Attitude.

00:18:41.370 --> 00:18:42.620
JASON ANDREAS: Yeah, maybe
we'll get, yeah, attitude.

