2010 I was just
scouring the state,

00:19:16.890 --> 00:19:19.155
physically visiting
a lot of places,

00:19:19.155 --> 00:19:20.270
to Chicago, to New York.

00:19:20.270 --> 00:19:20.920
I went and visited.

00:19:20.920 --> 00:19:22.711
I want to know where
everything comes from.

