They're like a very
high-standard broker

00:19:31.560 --> 00:19:35.050
of farm animals, mushrooms
across the country.

00:19:35.050 --> 00:19:37.150
So if I want the best
bison America has to offer,

00:19:37.150 --> 00:19:39.300
D'Artagnan, they broker it.

00:19:39.300 --> 00:19:43.470
And they list their farms and
their network of accountability

00:19:43.470 --> 00:19:45.030
that chefs can contact into.

00:19:45.030 --> 00:19:48.150
So I met that caliber of
I guess my career, where

00:19:48.150 --> 00:19:50.400
I can tap into the best
network in America.

